---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-6">About DiscussAI</h1>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-6">
            DiscussAI was created with a simple yet powerful mission: to foster deeper understanding through guided conversations that present multiple perspectives.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
          <p>
            In today's world of information overload and echo chambers, we believe in the power of thoughtful dialogue to expand minds and build bridges. Our AI-guided discussions create a space where ideas can be explored from different angles, helping members develop more nuanced perspectives on complex topics.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">How It Works</h2>
          <p>
            Our platform pairs you with two AI hosts who present different viewpoints on your chosen topic. These hosts are designed to be knowledgeable, respectful, and thought-provoking. You participate in the conversation through voice interaction, creating a natural and engaging experience.
          </p>
          <p>
            Each discussion lasts approximately 7 minutes, during which you'll be invited to contribute 3-5 times. After the conversation, you'll receive a summary and transcript, allowing you to reflect on the insights gained.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Values</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Intellectual Curiosity:</strong> We believe in the power of asking questions and exploring ideas.</li>
            <li><strong>Respectful Dialogue:</strong> All perspectives are treated with respect, even when there's disagreement.</li>
            <li><strong>Diverse Viewpoints:</strong> We value the richness that comes from considering multiple angles.</li>
            <li><strong>Continuous Learning:</strong> We're committed to the ongoing pursuit of knowledge and understanding.</li>
            <li><strong>Ethical Technology:</strong> We develop and use AI in ways that benefit humanity and respect human dignity.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Join Us</h2>
          <p>
            Whether you're looking to deepen your understanding of familiar topics or explore new areas of knowledge, DiscussAI offers a unique opportunity to engage with ideas in a meaningful way. Join our community of curious minds today.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12">
          <a href="/membership" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary-600 to-primary-600 rounded-lg font-medium text-white hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity shadow-lg">
            Become a Member
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
